stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> MainTreeOnly
    MainTreeOnly --> PendingGrowing: fastupdate=on 的 DML
    PendingGrowing --> PendingGrowing: 追加条目
    PendingGrowing --> Cleaning: Vacuum/Autoanalyze/函数/超过阈值
    Cleaning --> MainTreeOnly: 排序并合并完成
    PendingGrowing --> DirectMainInsert: fastupdate 关闭后的新 DML
    DirectMainInsert --> DirectMainInsert
    DirectMainInsert --> MainTreeOnly: 显式清理旧 Pending
